 *   • Backward compat: legacy serial_number CPTs without a sn_pool row continue
 *     to work — sn_pool sync hook is best-effort + non-blocking.
 * Version: V.30.4 (2026-04-24) — Phase 4e Module Registry adoption (Pillar 1):
 *   • Self-register via dinoco_register_admin_module() at init priority 30.
 *     key=transfer, shortcode=dinoco_admin_transfer, section=inventory, cache_ttl=300.
