 *                 Fix: emit nonce as inline JS variable inside the shortcode render
 *                 (regenerates per page load — bypasses 5min module cache since
 *                 wp_create_nonce() is called fresh on each shortcode invocation —
 *                 the cache contains the JS var with that page-load's nonce, which
 *                 is still valid for the standard nonce lifetime [12-24hr] — well
